Output demo.mp4

Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1600
Set Height 900
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 60ms

Hide
Type "cd ~"
Enter
Show

Type "tmux"
Enter
Sleep 1s
Type "cowrite draft.md --with claude"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Ctrl+B
Type o

Sleep 1s
Type "read ./draft.md, tighten up the second paragraph"
Enter
Sleep 20s

Ctrl+B
Type o
Sleep 3s
